#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:167
msgid ""
"The :ref:`Profit and Loss <accounting/reporting/profit-and-loss>` statement "
"shows details of income and expenses."
msgstr ""
"Het\\ :ref:`Winst- en verliesoverzicht <accounting/reporting/profit-and-"
"loss>`\\ toont details van inkomsten en uitgaven."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:175
msgid ""
"The :ref:`Balance Sheet <accounting/reporting/balance-sheet>` summarizes the "
"company's assets, liabilities, and equity at a specific time."
msgstr ""
"De\\ :ref:`Balans <accounting/reporting/balance-sheet>`\\ vat de activa, "
"passiva en eigen vermogen van het bedrijf op een specifiek moment samen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:3
msgid "Cash discounts and tax reduction"
msgstr "Contantkortingen en belastingvermindering"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:5
msgid ""
"**Cash discounts** are reductions in the amount a customer must pay for "
"goods or services offered as an incentive for paying their invoice promptly. "
"These discounts are typically a percentage of the total invoice amount and "
"are applied if the customer pays within a specified time. Cash discounts can "
"help a company maintain a steady cash flow."
msgstr ""
"**Contantkortingen** zijn verminderingen in het bedrag dat een klant moet "
"betalen voor goederen of diensten, aangeboden als stimulans om hun factuur "
"snel te betalen. Deze kortingen zijn doorgaans een percentage van het totale "
"factuurbedrag en worden toegepast als de klant binnen een bepaalde tijd "
"betaalt. Contantkortingen kunnen een bedrijf helpen een stabiele kasstroom "
"te behouden."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:11
msgid ""
"You issue a €100 invoice on the 1st of January. The full payment is due "
"within 30 days, and you also offer a 2% discount if your customer pays you "
"within seven days."
msgstr ""
"Je stuurt een factuur van €100 op 1 januari. De volledige betaling moet "
"binnen 30 dagen plaatsvinden, en je biedt ook 2% korting aan als je klant "
"binnen zeven dagen betaalt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:14
msgid ""
"The customer can pay €98 up to the 8th of January. After that date, they "
"would have to pay €100 by the 31st of January."
msgstr ""
"De klant kan tot 8 januari €98 betalen. Na die datum zou hij/zij €100 moeten "
"betalen vóór 31 januari."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:17
msgid ""
"A :ref:`tax reduction <cash-discounts/tax-reductions>` can also be applied "
"depending on the country or region."
msgstr ""
"Een\\ :ref:`belastingvermindering <cash-discounts/tax-reductions>`\\ kan ook "
"worden toegepast, afhankelijk van het land of de regio."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:21
msgid ":doc:`payment_terms`"
msgstr ":doc:`payment_terms`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:22
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:23
msgid ":doc:`../payments`"
msgstr ":doc:`../payments`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:29
msgid ""
"To grant cash discounts to customers, you must first verify the :ref:`gain "
"and loss accounts <cash-discounts/gain-loss-accounts>`. Then, "
"configure :ref:`payment terms <cash-discounts/payment-terms>` and add a cash "
"discount by checking the :guilabel:`Early Discount` checkbox and filling in "
"the discount percentage, discount days, and :ref:`tax reduction <cash-"
"discounts/tax-reductions>` fields."
msgstr ""
"Om contantkortingen aan klanten te geven, moet je eerst de\\ :ref:`winst- en "
"verliesrekeningen <cash-discounts/gain-loss-accounts>`\\ verifiëren. "
"Configureer vervolgens\\ :ref:`betalingsvoorwaarden <cash-discounts/payment-"
"terms>`\\ en voeg een contantkorting toe door het "
"selectievakje\\ :guilabel:`Vroege korting`\\ aan te vinken en het "
"kortingspercentage, kortingsdagen en\\ :ref:`belastingvermindering <cash-"
"discounts/tax-reductions>`\\ in te vullen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:38
msgid "Cash discount gain/loss accounts"
msgstr "Winst-/verliesrekeningen voor contantkorting"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:40
msgid ""
"With a cash discount, the amount you earn depends on whether the customer "
"benefits from the cash discount or not. This inevitably leads to gains and "
"losses, which are recorded on default accounts."
msgstr ""
"Met een contantkorting hangt het bedrag dat je verdient ervan af of de klant "
"gebruikmaakt van de contantkorting of niet. Dit leidt onvermijdelijk tot "
"winsten en verliezen, die worden geregistreerd op standaardrekeningen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:43
msgid ""
"To modify these accounts, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration "
"--> Settings`, and, in the :guilabel:`Default Accounts` section, select the "
"accounts you want to use for the :guilabel:`Cash Discount Gain account` "
"and :guilabel:`Cash Discount Loss account`."
msgstr ""
"Om deze rekeningen te wijzigen, ga je naar\\ :menuselection:`Boekhouding --> "
"Configuratie --> Instellingen`, en selecteer je in het "
"gedeelte\\ :guilabel:`Standaardrekeningen`\\ de rekeningen die je wilt "
"gebruiken voor de\\ :guilabel:`Winstrekening contantkorting`\\ "
"en\\ :guilabel:`Verliesrekening contantkorting`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:50
msgid "Payment terms"
msgstr "Betaalvoorwaarden"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:52
msgid ""
"Cash discounts are defined on :doc:`payment terms <payment_terms>`. "
"Configure them to your liking by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Payment Terms`, and make sure to fill out the discount "
"percentage, discount days, and :ref:`tax reduction <cash-discounts/tax-"
"reductions>` fields."
msgstr ""
"Contantkortingen worden gedefinieerd op\\ :doc:`betalingsvoorwaarden "
"<payment_terms>`. Configureer ze naar wens door te gaan "
"naar\\ :menuselection:`Boekhouding --> Configuratie --> "
"Betalingsvoorwaarden`, en zorg ervoor dat je het kortingspercentage, "
"kortingsdagen en\\ :ref:`belastingvermindering <cash-discounts/tax-"
"reductions>`\\ invult."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:None
msgid ""
"Configuration of payment terms named \"2/7 Net 30\". The field \"Description "
"on Invoices\"\n"
"reads: \"Payment terms: 30 Days, 2% Early Payment Discount under 7 days\"."
msgstr ""
"Configuratie van betalingsvoorwaarden genaamd \"2/7 Netto 30\". Het veld "
"\"Omschrijving op facturen\" luidt: \"Betalingsvoorwaarden: 30 dagen, 2% "
"korting bij vroege betaling binnen 7 dagen\"."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:64
msgid "Tax reductions"
msgstr "Belastingverminderingen"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:66
msgid ""
"Depending on the country or region, the base amount used to compute the tax "
"can vary, which can lead to a **tax reduction**. Since tax reductions are "
"set on individual payment terms, each term can use a specific tax reduction."
msgstr ""
"Afhankelijk van het land of de regio kan het basisbedrag dat gebruikt wordt "
"om de belasting te berekenen variëren, wat kan leiden tot een "
"**belastingvermindering**. Omdat belastingverminderingen worden ingesteld op "
"individuele betalingsvoorwaarden, kan elke voorwaarde een specifieke "
"belastingvermindering gebruiken."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:70
msgid ""
"To configure how the tax reduction is applied, go to a payment term with "
"the :guilabel:`Early Discount` checkbox enabled, and select one of the three "
"following options:"
msgstr ""
"Om te configureren hoe de belastingvermindering wordt toegepast, ga je naar "
"betalingsvoorwaarden met het selectievakje :guilabel:`Vroege korting` "
"ingeschakeld en selecteer je een van de volgende drie opties:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:75
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:94
msgid "Always (upon invoice)"
msgstr "Altijd (op factuur)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:74
msgid ""
"The tax is always reduced. The base amount used to compute the tax is the "
"discounted amount, whether the customer benefits from the discount or not."
msgstr ""
"De belasting wordt altijd verminderd. Het basisbedrag dat gebruikt wordt om "
"de belasting te berekenen is het kortingsbedrag, ongeacht of de klant "
"profiteert van de korting of niet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:80
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:109
msgid "On early payment"
msgstr "Bij vroege betaling"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:78
msgid ""
"The tax is reduced only if the customer pays early. The base amount used to "
"compute the tax is the same as the sale: if the customer benefits from the "
"reduction, then the tax is reduced. This means that, depending on the "
"customer, the tax amount can vary after the invoice is issued."
msgstr ""
"De belasting wordt alleen verminderd als de klant vroeg betaalt. Het "
"basisbedrag dat gebruikt wordt om de belasting te berekenen is hetzelfde als "
"de verkoop: als de klant profiteert van de korting, dan wordt de belasting "
"verminderd. Dit betekent dat, afhankelijk van de klant, het belastingbedrag "
"kan variëren nadat de factuur is uitgegeven."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:84
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:124
msgid "Never"
msgstr "Nooit"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:83
msgid ""
"The tax is never reduced. The base amount used to compute the tax is the "
"full amount, whether the customer benefits from the discount or not."
msgstr ""
"De belasting wordt nooit verminderd. Het basisbedrag dat gebruikt wordt om "
"de belasting te berekenen is het volledige bedrag, ongeacht of de klant "
"profiteert van de korting of niet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:88
msgid ""
"You issue a €100 invoice (tax-excluded) on the 1st of January, with a 21% "
"tax rate. The full payment is due within 30 days, and you also offer a 2% "
"discount if your customer pays you within seven days."
msgstr ""
"Je geeft een factuur van €100 (exclusief belasting) uit op 1 januari, met "
"een btw-tarief van 21%. De volledige betaling is verschuldigd binnen 30 "
"dagen, en je biedt ook 2% korting aan als je klant je binnen zeven dagen "
"betaalt."

