"the :guilabel:`My Expenses` dashboard, by default. Alternatively, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> My Expenses --> My Expenses`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/expense_reports.rst:10
