msgstr "Voeg het label 281-50 toe aan een contactformulier"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:211
msgid "CODA and SODA statements"
msgstr "CODA- en SODA-bestanden"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:216
msgid "CODA"
msgstr "CODA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:218
msgid ""
"**CODA** is an electronic XML format used to import Belgian bank statements. "
"You can download CODA files from your bank and import them directly into "
"Odoo by clicking :guilabel:`Import file` from your :guilabel:`Bank` journal "
"on your dashboard."
msgstr ""
"**CODA** is een elektronisch XML-formaat dat wordt gebruikt om Belgische "
"bankafschriften te importeren. Je kunt CODA-bestanden downloaden van je bank "
"en ze direct in Odoo importeren door te klikken op :guilabel:`Bestand "
"importeren` vanuit je :guilabel:`Bank`-dagboek op je dashboard."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "Import CODA files"
msgstr "CODA-bestanden importeren"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:226
msgid ":ref:`Import bank files <transactions/import>`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:231
msgid "SODA"
msgstr "SODA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:233
msgid ""
"**SODA** is an electronic XML format used to import accounting entries "
"related to salaries. SODA files can be imported into the journal you use to "
"record salaries by going to your Accounting **dashboard** and "
"clicking :guilabel:`Upload` in the related journal card form."
msgstr ""
"**SODA** is een elektronisch XML-formaat dat gebruikt wordt om "
"boekhoudkundige boekingen gerelateerd aan salarissen te importeren. SODA-"
"bestanden kunnen geïmporteerd worden in het dagboek dat je gebruikt om "
"salarissen vast te leggen door naar je **Boekhouding-dashboard** te gaan en "
"op :guilabel:`Uploaden` te klikken in het bijbehorende dagboekkaartformulier."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:237
msgid ""
"Once your **SODA** files are imported, the entries are created automatically "
"in your salary journal."
msgstr ""
"Zodra je **SODA**-bestanden zijn geïmporteerd, worden de boekingen "
"automatisch aangemaakt in je salarisdagboek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "Import SODA files"
msgstr "SODA-bestanden importeren"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:245
msgid "CodaBox"
msgstr "CodaBox"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:247
msgid ""
"**CodaBox** is a service that allows Belgian companies and accounting firms "
"to access bank information and statements. Odoo provides a way to import "
"such statements automatically."
msgstr ""
"**CodaBox** is een service waarmee Belgische bedrijven en boekhoudkantoren "
"toegang krijgen tot bankinformatie en bankafschriften. Odoo biedt een manier "
"om dergelijke afschriften automatisch te importeren."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:253
msgid ""
"To configure and use Codabox, first :ref:`install <general/install>` "
"the :guilabel:`CodaBox` module."
msgstr ""
"Om Codabox te configureren en te gebruiken, :ref:`installeer <general/"
"install>` je eerst de :guilabel:`CodaBox`-module."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:258
msgid "Configure the Connection"
msgstr "De verbinding configureren"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:262
msgid "For companies"
msgstr "Voor bedrijven"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:265
msgid ""
"Make sure the :doc:`company settings </applications/general/companies>` are "
"correctly configured, i.e., the country is set to :guilabel:`Belgium` and "
"the :guilabel:`Tax ID` or :guilabel:`Company ID` field is filled."
msgstr ""
"Zorg ervoor dat de :doc:`bedrijfsinstellingen </applications/general/"
"companies>` correct zijn, d.w.z. dat het land is ingesteld op "
":guilabel:`België` en het veld :guilabel:`Btw-nummer` of :guilabel:`Bedrijfs-"
"ID` is ingevuld."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:269
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:298
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`, then go to "
"the :guilabel:`CodaBox & SODA` section."
msgstr ""
"Ga naar :menuselection:`Boekhouding --> Configuratie --> Instellingen` en ga "
"vervolgens naar het gedeelte :guilabel:`CodaBox & SODA`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:271
msgid ""
"Click on :guilabel:`Manage Connection` to open the connection wizard, which "
"shows the :guilabel:`Company VAT/ID` number that will be used for the "
"connection."
msgstr ""
"Klik op :guilabel:`Verbinding beheren` om de verbindingswizard te openen, "
"die het :guilabel:`Bedrijfs-btw/ID`-nummer toont dat voor de verbinding "
"wordt gebruikt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:273
msgid ""
"If this is your **first connection**, click on :guilabel:`Create "
"connection`. The wizard confirms that the connection has been created on "
"**Odoo's side**. Follow the steps to validate the connection on **CodaBox's "
"side** too."
msgstr ""
"Als dit je **eerste verbinding** is, klik dan op :guilabel:`Verbinding "
"aanmaken`. De wizard bevestigt dat de verbinding aan **Odoo's kant** is "
"aangemaakt. Volg de stappen om de verbinding ook aan **CodaBox's kant** te "
"valideren."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:277
msgid ""
"If this is **not your first connection**, the :guilabel:`Password` provided "
"by Odoo during the first connection will be requested to create a new "
"connection."
msgstr ""
"Als dit **niet je eerste verbinding** is, wordt het :guilabel:`Wachtwoord` "
"gevraagd dat Odoo tijdens de eerste verbinding heeft verstrekt om een nieuwe "
"verbinding aan te maken."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:281
msgid ""
"This :guilabel:`Password` is unique to Odoo and must be stored securely on "
"your side."
msgstr ""
"Dit :guilabel:`Wachtwoord` is uniek voor Odoo en moet veilig door jou worden "
"bewaard."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:284
msgid "For accounting firms"
msgstr "Voor accountantskantoren"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:286
msgid ""
"Accounting firms must manage their clients on separate databases and "
"configure them individually to avoid mixing up their data. The connection "
"must be made by an accounting firm with valid CodaBox Connect credentials. "
"In the following instructions, we will refer to your client's company as "
"*Company* and to your accounting firm as *Accounting Firm*."
msgstr ""
"Accountantskantoren moeten hun klanten op afzonderlijke databases beheren en "
"deze individueel configureren om vermenging van gegevens te voorkomen. De "
"verbinding moet worden gemaakt door een accountantskantoor met geldige "
"CodaBox Connect-inloggegevens. In de volgende instructies verwijzen we naar "
"het bedrijf van je klant als *Bedrijf* en naar je accountantskantoor als "
"*Accountantskantoor*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:293
msgid ""
"Make sure the :doc:`company settings </applications/general/companies>` are "
"correctly configured, i.e., the country is set to :guilabel:`Belgium`, "
"the :guilabel:`Tax ID` or :guilabel:`Company ID` and :guilabel:`Accounting "
"Firm` fields are filled, as well as the :guilabel:`Tax ID` of "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting Firm`."
msgstr ""
"Zorg dat de :doc:`bedrijfsinstellingen </applications/general/companies>` "
"correct zijn geconfigureerd, d.w.z. het land is ingesteld "
"op :guilabel:`België`, de velden :guilabel:`Btw-ID` of :guilabel:`Bedrijfs-"
"ID` en :guilabel:`Accountantskantoor` zijn ingevuld, evenals "
"de :guilabel:`Btw-ID` van het :guilabel:`Accountantskantoor`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:300
msgid ""
"Click on :guilabel:`Manage Connection` to open the connection wizard, which "
"shows the :guilabel:`Accounting Firm VAT` number and the :guilabel:`Company "
"VAT/ID` number that will be used for the connection."
msgstr ""
"Klik op :guilabel:`Verbinding beheren` om de verbindingswizard te openen, "
"die het :guilabel:`Btw-nummer accountantskantoor` en het :guilabel:`Bedrijfs-"
"btw/ID`-nummer toont dat voor de verbinding wordt gebruikt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:303
msgid ""
"If this is your **first connection**, click on :guilabel:`Create "
"connection`. The wizard confirms that the connection has been created on "
"**Odoo's side**. Follow the steps to validate the connection on **CodaBox's "
"side**, too."
msgstr ""
"Als dit je **eerste verbinding** is, klik dan op :guilabel:`Verbinding "
"aanmaken`. De wizard bevestigt dat de verbinding aan **Odoo's kant** is "
"aangemaakt. Volg de stappen om de verbinding ook aan **CodaBox's kant** te "
"valideren."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:307
msgid ""
"If this is **not your first connection**, the :guilabel:`Accounting Firm "
"Password` provided by Odoo during the first connection will be requested to "
"create a new connection."
msgstr ""
"Als dit **niet je eerste verbinding** is, wordt het :guilabel:`Wachtwoord "
"accountantskantoor` gevraagd dat Odoo tijdens de eerste verbinding heeft "
"verstrekt om een nieuwe verbinding aan te maken."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:311
msgid ""
"This :guilabel:`Accounting Firm Password` is unique to Odoo and must be "
"stored securely on your side."
msgstr ""
"Dit :guilabel:`Wachtwoord accountantskantoor` is uniek voor Odoo en moet "
"veilig door jou worden bewaard."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:314
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Status` should have now switched to :guilabel:`Connected`."
msgstr ""
"De :guilabel:`Status` zou nu moeten zijn veranderd "
"naar :guilabel:`Verbonden`."

