#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:62
msgid "Tax exemption"
msgstr "Belastingvrijstelling"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:64
msgid ""
"The use of sale taxes that amount to **zero percent** (0%) is required by "
"Italian authorities to keep track of the exact :guilabel:`Tax Exemption Kind "
"(Natura)` and :guilabel:`Law Reference` that justify the exemption operated "
"on an invoice line."
msgstr ""
"Het gebruik van verkoopbtw met een tarief van **nul procent** (0%) is "
"vereist door de Italiaanse autoriteiten om het exacte :guilabel:`Type btw-"
"vrijstelling (Natura)` en de :guilabel:`Wettelijke referentie` bij te houden "
"die de vrijstelling op een factuurregel rechtvaardigen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:69
msgid ""
"The export tax in the EU can be used as reference (`0% EU`, invoice label "
"`00eu`). It can be found under :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration "
"--> Taxes`. Exports are exempt from VAT, and therefore, they "
"require :guilabel:`Exoneration` kind and :guilabel:`Law Reference` filled in."
msgstr ""
"De exportbtw in de EU kan als referentie worden gebruikt (`0% EU`, "
"facturatieopschrift `00eu`). Deze is te vinden "
"onder :menuselection:`Boekhouding --> Configuratie --> btw`. Export is "
"vrijgesteld van btw en daarom moeten het :guilabel:`Vrijstellingstype` en "
"de :guilabel:`Wettelijke referentie` worden ingevuld."

