msgstr "XAF-export"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/netherlands.rst:8
msgid ""
"With the Dutch accounting localization installed, you will be able to export "
"all your accounting entries in XAF format. For this, you have to go "
"in :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> General Ledger`, you define "
"the entries you want to export using the filters (period, journals, ...) and "
"then you click on the button **EXPORT (XAF)**."
msgstr ""
"Met de Nederlandse boekhoudinglokalisatie geïnstalleerd, kun je al je "
"boekingen exporteren in XAF-formaat. Hiervoor ga je "
"naar :menuselection:`Boekhouding --> Rapportage --> Grootboek`, definieer je "
"de boekingen die je wilt exporteren met behulp van de filters (periode, "
"dagboeken, ...) en klik je op de knop **EXPORTEREN (XAF)**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/netherlands.rst:15
msgid "Dutch Accounting Reports"
msgstr "Nederlandse boekhoudkundige rapporten"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/netherlands.rst:17
msgid ""
"If you install the Dutch accounting localization, you will have access to "
"some reports that are specific to the Netherlands such as :"
msgstr ""
"Als je de Nederlandse boekhoudinglokalisatie installeert, krijg je toegang "
"tot enkele rapporten die specifiek zijn voor Nederland, zoals:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/netherlands.rst:21
msgid "Tax Report (Aangifte omzetbelasting)"
msgstr "Btw-aangifte (Aangifte omzetbelasting)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/netherlands.rst:22
