msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dagboek`: selecteer het dagboek dat elektronisch moet zijn en de "
"optie :guilabel:`Documenten gebruiken?` actief heeft."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:320
msgid ":guilabel:`Document Type`: select the credit note document type."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Documenttype`: selecteer het creditfactuurdocumenttype."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:326
msgid ""
"The :doc:`Customer debit note <../accounting/customer_invoices/"
"credit_notes>` is an electronic document that, when validated, is sent to |"
"DGI| via Uruware. It is necessary to have a validated (posted) invoice to "
"register a debit note. On the invoice, click the :icon:`fa-cog` "
