"Configuration --> Bank Accounts` en selecteer de bankrekening. Vul de "
"velden :guilabel:`Bank Identifier Code`, :guilabel:`Proxy Type` (gebaseerd "
"op de informatie die wordt gebruikt om de :guilabel:`Merchant Account` te "
"identificeren, zoals het kaartnummer en bankrekeningnummers) "
"en :guilabel:`Proxy Value` in."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:253
msgid ""
"Enable :guilabel:`Include Reference` to include the invoice number in the QR "
"code."
msgstr ""
"Schakel :guilabel:`Include Reference` in om het factuurnummer in de QR-code "
"op te nemen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:256
msgid ""
"The account holder's country must be set to `Vietnam`, and their city must "
"be specified on the contact form."
msgstr ""
"Het land van de rekeninghouder moet zijn ingesteld op `Vietnam` en hun stad "
"moet worden gespecificeerd op het contactformulier."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:258
msgid ""
"The :ref:`account number <accounting/bank/account-number>` and bank must be "
"set on the :guilabel:`Bank` journal."
