#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:265
msgid "Generating QR codes on invoices"
msgstr "QR-codes genereren op facturen"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:267
msgid ""
"When creating a new invoice, open the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab and "
"select :guilabel:`EMV Merchant-Presented QR-code` in the :guilabel:`Payment "
"QR-code` field."
msgstr ""
"Open bij het aanmaken van een nieuwe factuur het tabblad :guilabel:`Other "
"Info` en selecteer :guilabel:`EMV Merchant-Presented QR-code` in het "
"veld :guilabel:`Payment QR-code`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:271
msgid ""
"Ensure the :guilabel:`Recipient Bank` is configured, as Odoo uses this field "
"to generate QR codes."
msgstr ""
"Zorg ervoor dat de :guilabel:`Recipient Bank` is geconfigureerd, aangezien "
"Odoo dit veld gebruikt om QR-codes te genereren."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:30
msgid ""
"Odoo embeds several **payment providers** that allow your customers to pay "
"online, on their *customer portals*, or on your *eCommerce website*. They "
"can pay sales orders, invoices, or subscriptions with recurring payments "
"using their favorite payment methods, such as **credit cards**."
msgstr ""
"Odoo bevat verschillende **betaalproviders** waarmee je klanten online "
"kunnen betalen, op hun *klantportalen* of op je *e-commercewebsite*. Ze "
"kunnen verkooporders, facturen of abonnementen met terugkerende betalingen "
"betalen met hun favoriete betaalmethoden, zoals **creditcards**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:35
msgid ""
"Each payment provider is linked to a list of supported :ref:`payment methods "
"<payment_providers/payment_methods>` that can be (de)activated based on your "
"needs."
msgstr ""
"Elke betaalprovider is gekoppeld aan een lijst met "
"ondersteunde :ref:`payment methods <payment_providers/payment_methods>` die "
"kunnen worden (de)geactiveerd op basis van je behoeften."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:None
msgid "Online payment form"
msgstr "Onlinebetalingsformulier"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:42
msgid ""
"Odoo apps delegate the handling of sensitive information to the certified "
"payment provider so that you don't ever have to worry about PCI compliance. "
"No sensitive information (such as credit card numbers) is stored on Odoo "
"servers or Odoo databases hosted elsewhere. Instead, Odoo apps use a unique "
"reference number for the data stored safely in the payment providers' "
"systems."
msgstr ""
"Odoo-apps delegeren de verwerking van gevoelige informatie aan de "
"gecertificeerde betaalprovider, zodat je je nooit zorgen hoeft te maken over "
"PCI-compliance. Geen gevoelige informatie (zoals creditcardnummers) wordt "
"opgeslagen op Odoo-servers of Odoo-databases die elders worden gehost. In "
"plaats daarvan gebruiken Odoo-apps een uniek referentienummer voor de "
"gegevens die veilig zijn opgeslagen in de systemen van de betaalproviders."

